title: General Biology 1: For Senior High School (Specialized Subject)
author: Ruben E. Faltado III, Reneecilia B. Paz de Leon, Merle B. Lopez
description: A senior high school biology textbook covering cellular and molecular biology: cell theory, cell structure and function, transport mechanisms, biological molecules, energy transformation, and related foundational biology concepts. 128 pages. Published by Lorimar Publishing, Inc.
